{
  "stem": "15578.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But nevertheless, a lot of people didn't survive there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The whole camp, I think, was about 5,000 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But everyday, they come from other camps, and then go what people die.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I-- when I was the cook, I worked with some-- with some Russian people, Ukraine, and Polish people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had a few Jewish people there, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one time there come another [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] head of the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "His name was Stibitz-- a very bad man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then another chief in the cook-- in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they threw it out, all the Jewish people from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was one of them, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we were very good to each other in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When they threw me out, then some other people helped me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But nevertheless, I had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When I went-- so they put me in in a commando where-- outside, I would say a kilometer or a kilometer and a half from the camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When you went out from the camp, you turn to the left, and go as far-- there was a-- a little forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then you turn again to the left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- and about 50 yards from there was dig a grave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I would say almost as big as a hockey arena.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the deep was about-- I would say about 15 feet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I had to work there not for long-- I think it was for about a week.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "What they brought in that people, and we had to sort them out in the grave and put them like sardines.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The head between the legs.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
